Account Manager - Digital Marketing Agency
Company Name Confidential
Share this job
Apply
Job Description Account Manager (Agency-side)Based in SingaporeAbout the CompanyOur Client is an award-winning, global digital marketing agency with international offices.They connect brands to their audiences with relevant and meaningful experiences, delivered across multiple channels and touch points.Role SummaryWe are looking for an experienced Account Manager to join our Singapore team. The Account Manager has a focus in the IT/Tech industries on a wide variety of projects which span from customer evidence programs to social media campaigns.The ideal candidate will be able to successfully manage a wide array of projects, resources, and budgets while exceeding client expectations and driving new business opportunities.Specific ResponsibilitiesAbility to meet and exceed annual revenue goalManage multiple, large-budget projects simultaneouslyBuild long-lasting relationships with clients and recognize opportunities to grow business existing accountsAbility to write/prepare statements of work, requests for proposals and other pitch materialsCan clearly communicate complex ideasAbility to quickly ramp up on client’s business needs and know the right questions to ask to get to the heart of how we can help themAbility to take ownership of projects and accounts and feel empowered to make smart, well-thought out decisionsAt the end of the day you need to be able to creatively solve problems and be able to see the big picture and how everything we do fits together. You need to anticipate your client’s needs and be ready with solutions. You need to understand your client’s end game and what will make him/her successful.Ideally, you would have had similar agency-side experience serving the IT/Tech industries.How to ApplyCandidates in Singapore are welcome to send their CVs tocandidate-support@executivesearch.asia with their current and expected salary information and notice period. We regret to say that this position is open to Singaporeans or PRs only.Asia Williams Pte. Ltd.Singapore EA 12S5970Follow us on LinkedIn: http://goo.gl/NoEEaLike us on Facebook: http://goo.gl/KvMM9+1 on GooglePlus: http://goo.gl/zDKSR1
